The only difference is we've added a little bit of documentation

00:32:16.000 --> 00:32:20.000
so that the R wrapper functions that are generated have documentation.

00:32:20.000 --> 00:32:25.000
And, actually, why don't we just convince ourselves that these things do have documentation.

